<plot>Kevin, a narcissistic, fading movie actor, meets with John, a visually impaired man, the subject of his newest film. When both men discover a truth highlighted by the other- John's story has been cheapened by Kevin's Hollywood colleagues; John has withheld the real cause of his blindness, a bizarre inexplicable accident- the pair clash over the erratic, uncontrollable nature of life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?055988</url></doc>
